	<h1>Pricing</h1>
<p>
	Ratafire’s prices are designed to ensure the creators or researchers receive the base amount of the subscription. We use Amazon Payments as our payment method.
</p>

<p>
	Once you subscribe to another user, you will be charged the first month's subscription fee. We will charge the subscriber the Total amount. During the transaction, Amazon Payments will collect transaction fees, and Ratafire will take from 3% to 9% percent of the total amount depending on the amount. Creators or researchers will receive the amount stated in the Receives at Least row.
</p>

<p>
  Except from the first price level of Supporter, all other prices are for Subscriber. These two categories of users will receive different benefits.  
</p> 
